{"tid":1334751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果堅既，勇武，唔應該割如果犬老屈，更唔應該割初步推論有以下幾個疑點","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:43:47.000Z","uid":281463,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e449f1f907edde299b82fa97979202d2c28905bc","tid":1334751,"uid":281463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmvqdPT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmvqdPT.jpg&h=000692f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTATP 240ml足以炸毀一架飛機<br />\n堅係高殺傷力班撚屌犬點會拗埋手氣定神閒睇引爆呢？<br />\n一公斤威力應好大，我地睇睇犬隻的巧妙安排<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑點一：<br />\n犬話跟左幾個月，造炸彈咁大劑就應該早早拉人封艇，使等7.20前夕湊夠一公斤先拉？<br />\n<br />\n疑點二：<br />\n7.20早上7：00第一次引爆<br />\n7：00引爆已知危險，點解之後會畀人入大廈返工既？<br />\n<br />\n疑點三：<br />\n承疑點二，7.20  11：55先疏散人群，<br />\n星期六好多藍領開工架！<br />\n13：20先二度引爆，疏散和引爆不足兩小時<br />\n要疏散不可能用不足兩小時確認大廈每個單位都吉晒，<br />\n犬段鳩估，爆炸冧樓死人點算？<br />\n<br />\n但13：00氣定神閒已set定場call定記者開記招set定場開記招<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356060&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356060%26refer%3DShare&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=446a1851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356060%26refer%3DShare&h=5b16d2f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356060&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n疑點四：<br />\n7.19  22：30突擊撿查並話&rdquo;當場&rdquo;拉人<br />\n翌日早上六時先話有鐵通和爆炸品，<br />\n仲話粉末放係枱度咁易搵？<br />\n<br />\n由拉人到發現爆炸品7個幾鐘班犬係度做咩野？<br />\n呢段不短的時間內犬隔開當事人，現場有冇人及物資進入？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/354188/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%BA%AB-%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E6%AA%A2tatp%E7%83%88%E6%80%A7%E7%82%B8%E8%97%A5-%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-o%E8%A8%98%E8%B7%9F%E8%B9%A4%E6%8B%9827%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7\" data-sr-url=\"h